<item>
            <title>[SOLR-4352] Velocity-base pagination should support/preserve sorting</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-4352</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When performing /browse, the Velocity generated UI does not support sorting in the generated pagination links.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The link_to_previous_page and link_to_next_page macros found within &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;apache-solr-4.0.0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;/example/solr/collection1/conf/velocity/VM_global_library.vm should be modified to maintain/preserve an existing sort parameter.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12629164">SOLR-4352</key>
            <summary>Velocity-base pagination should support/preserve sorting</summary>
